OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK government debt on      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funsustainable path unless  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftaxes hiked, says OBR      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK debt is on an "unsustainable path"  
OL,6, unless spending is tightened and taxes 
OL,7, are raised, the government's           
OL,8, independent forecaster has warned.     
OL,10,FThe Office for Budget Responsibility   
OL,11,F(OBR) said soaring energy prices and   
OL,12,Fpressures from an ageing population    
OL,13,Frisked tipping the UK into a recession.
OL,15,FIt forecast debt levels could more than
OL,16,Ftreble in 50 years' time.              
OL,18,FHigh inflation is driving up interest  
OL,19,Fpayments. In May they hit #7.6bn, the  
OL,20,Fhighest level for that month on record.
